{"slug":"super-cop-top-cop","title":{"en":"Super Cop Top Cop","km":"ប៉ូលីសកំពូលប៉ូលីស"},"description":{"en":"After miraculously surviving a near-fatal gunshot wound, detective Fang Zhiqiang discovers he has gained extraordinary supernatural powers. While Zhiqiang uses his new abilities to fight crime, his close friend and colleague Chen Yixian becomes consumed by jealousy, fracturing their friendship and leading to a superpowered clash.","km":"ក្រោយពីបានរស់រានមានជីវិតពីការត្រូវគ្រាប់កាំភ្លើងយ៉ាងអស្ចារ្យ មន្ត្រីប៉ូលីស ហ្វាង ជីឈាង (Canti Lau) បានរកឃើញថាខ្លួនមានអំណាចពិសេសពីធម្មជាតិ។ ភាពលេចធ្លោរបស់គាត់បានធ្វើឱ្យមិត្តរួមការងារដ៏ស្និទ្ធស្នាល ឆិន អ៊ីសាន (Roger Kwok) កើតចិត្តច្រណែនយ៉ាងខ្លាំង រហូតដល់ក្លាយជាសត្រូវប្រយុទ្ធគ្នាយ៉ាងស៊ីសាច់ហុតឈាម។"},"poster":"https://i.mydramalist.com/EYq15f.jpg","year":1993,"rating":6.6,"genres":["ACTION","COMEDY","DRAMA","HORROR","ROMANCE","THRILLER","FANTASY"],"language":"English","episodeCount":20,"episodes":[{"ep":"1","title":{"en":"Episode 1","km":"ភាគទី1"},"url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/iamcleanerkak/wivkai/refs/heads/d1/x/index.single","type":"M3U8","final":false},{"ep":"2","title":{"en":"Episode 2","km":"ភាគទី2"},"url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/iamcleanerkak/wivkai/refs/heads/d2/x/index.single","type":"M3U8","final":false},{"ep":"3","title":{"en":"Episode 3","km":"ភាគទី3"},"url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/iamcleanerkak/wivkai/refs/heads/d3/x/index.single","type":"M3U8","final":false},{"ep":"4","title":{"en":"Episode 4","km":"ភាគទី4"},"url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/iamcleanerkak/wivkai/refs/heads/d4/x/index.single","type":"M3U8","final":false},{"ep":"5","title":{"en":"Episode 5","km":"ភាគទី5"},"url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/iamcleanerkak/wivkai/refs/heads/d5/x/index.single","type":"M3U8","final":false},{"ep":"6","title":{"en":"Episode 6","km":"ភាគទី6"},"url":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/iamcleanerkak/wivkai/refs/heads/d6/x/index.single","type":"M3U8","final":false},{"ep":"7","title":{"e